  {
    "name": "Get Started",
    "settings": [
      {
        "type": "header",
        "content": "Thank you!"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": "Thanks for checking out the Unicorn theme."
      },
      {
        "type": "header",
        "content": "Theme trial"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": "Sadly, the Shopify software doesn't come with a feature for easily switching between different demo styles of a theme."
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": "1) Theme style. The theme offers five different styles to choose from. You can select your preferred style by navigating to Theme settings -> Theme style."
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": "2) Sections and section settings. You'll need to manually apply changes. Here are the most important places:"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": "- logo) Theme settings -> Layout -> Sticky header Type. Theme settings -> Logo."
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": "- navigation) Sections -> Header -> Icons menu -> Main navigation, Menu type"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": "- layout) Theme settings -> Layout -> Enable page width, Header Type on large screens."
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": "3) Still need help? [Search the user manual](https:\/\/mpithemes.gitbook.io\/unicorn-shopify-theme\/demo) or [Request a theme demo](https:\/\/mpithemes.ticksy.com\/article\/19975)"
      },
      {
        "type": "header",
        "content": "Resources"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": "[Shopify help center](https:\/\/help.shopify.com)"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": "[Theme user manual](https:\/\/mpithemes.gitbook.io\/unicorn-shopify-theme)"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": "[Theme icon list](https:\/\/unicorn-theme-valuable.mpthemes.net\/pages\/theme-icons)"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": "[Import theme settings](https:\/\/mpithemes.gitbook.io\/unicorn-shopify-theme\/demo#import-theme-files)"
      },
      {
        "type": "header",
        "content": "Get support"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": "[Submit a ticket](https:\/\/mpithemes.ticksy.com\/submit)"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": "Email me [support@mpthemes.net](mailto:support@mpthemes.net)"
      }
    ]
  },
